CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 29, 1958, pg. B18, reads: "Silver Year - Mr. and Mrs. Archie Dennis Sr. of Adams St., North Side, celebrated their 25th wedding anniversary, March 22, with a charming reception. Assisting in receiving the many relatives and friends were the Dennises' lovely daughter, Patricia, and their son, Bob. Aides were Mrs. Vastella Zeigler and Miss Norma J. Render. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. Dennis and Archie Dennis Sr. posed on their 25th wedding anniversary in their home, Adams Street, Northside
